Airports are the [[en/Manual/Stations]] for [[en/Manual/Aircraft#aircraft|airplanes]] and [[en/Manual/Aircraft#helicopters|helicopters]]. They also contain a hangar in which airplanes and helicopters can be built and serviced. For the different types of airports, see [[en/Manual/Airports]].